### Upstream data

Fixture and lineup data is mirrored from
[Rugby Xplorer](https://www.rugbyxplorer.com.au/) (Rugby Australia) and
remains the property of its respective rights-holders. This repository
republishes that data for the community on a best-effort basis; it is not
authoritative. If a club, league, or rights-holder asks for content to be
removed, open an issue and it will be taken down.

### Third-party assets

- Club crests are the trade marks of their respective clubs and are
  displayed here for identification only.
- The Norths Pirates / Tunks Park parking diagram and pitch layouts are
  used with credit to the community contributors who supplied them.

